snippet.title: The Crush House - Official Gameplay Overview | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Learn more about The Crush House, a new game where you choose a crush-worthy cast, try to keep your audience happy, and ensure your show stays on the air as you try to uncover the sinister secrets lurking below the surface of this thirst-person shooter.

The Crush House will be released on August 9, 2024 on PC. A demo is available now.
